item.title: Puzzling Head-to-Heads in Women's Tennis History
item.description: Last week we looked at some of the biggest mismatches in the men’s game. What does the same analysis tell us about the most baffling women’s head-to-heads?

item.title: Sizing Up Surprising Head-to-Heads
item.description: Why is it that some players seem to consistently underperform against certain opponents? And how could we measure the all-time most surprising head-to-heads in the game?
